org.polarsys.chess.chessmlprofile.SystemModel.STS

Interface STSPackage.Literals

  • Enclosing interface:
    STSPackage

    public static interface STSPackage.Literals
    Defines literals for the meta objects that represent
    • each class,
    • each feature of each class,
    • each enum,
    • and each data type
